trans-unit.source: Represents a collection of <see cref="T:System.CodeDom.CodeNamespace" /> objects.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeNamespaceCollection> class provides a simple collection object that can be used to store a set of <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeNamespace> objects.
